### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

###

### List all users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users

###

### Get user by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/1

###

### Get user by ID (not found)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/999

###

### Create a new user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ketaki",
  "email": "ketaki@example.com"
}

###

### Create user — missing fields (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "No Email"
}

###

### Update a user
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Akshad Jaiswal Updated",
  "email": "akshad.updated@example.com"
}

###

### Delete a user
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/2
